  Routers
       
       Router is a device which is used to forward data from pc (or any connected input device) to another LAN or WAN 
  
  Router Ports
        
        Router ports used to make communication with other devices
        
   Types of Router Ports
   
                 Interface
                 Line
    
    Interface
         
         Used for  connecting router with other device  
         
         1.Ethernet interfaces
           used to connect router with other devices
          
         2.Serial Interfaces
             used to connect router with other router
             
   
   Line
   
       Used for configure router 
       
      1.Console port
          used for direct configuration
             (ex)
               configure router with pc
 
       2.Auxillary port
           
           used for configure router via internet
      
       
             
